      "text": "Indexed\nfolder 90 - 150\nG-95\n\nhas changed. The percipient now stands, as it were, in the relation to the world that God does. (This sounds like the Hermetic transform, achieved through the alchemical wedding, the union of opposites from which the hierogamy occurs with the birth of the \"Golden Flower\" - hierogamy leading to the divine child known, too, to the Taoist alchemists. Viewed this way, the \"Golden Flower\" is God occurring in -as?- the person's own mind, + the divine illumination is relat",
